pageTitle: Prime Minister’s itinerary for Monday, January 27, 2020 | Prime Minister of Canada
articleHtml:
Note: All times local

Ottawa, Ontario

The Prime Minister will meet with the Incident Response Group.

Closed to media.

2:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will attend Question Period.

5:00 p.m. The Prime Minister will meet with the Interim President of Venezuela, Juan Guaidó.

Office of the Prime Minister
West Block
Parliament Hill

Notes for media:

  • Photo opportunity at the beginning of the meeting
  • Media are asked to arrive no later than 4:30 p.m.
